item.content:
Test patients for genetic variants of DPYD prior to initiating FAVLYXA unless immediate treatment is necessary. Avoid use of FAVLYXA in patients with certain homozygous or compound heterozygous DPYD variants that result in complete DPD deficiency [see 

                              Warnings and Precautions (5.1)

                           ].

text.paragraph:
FAVLYXA can cause fetal harm when administered to a pregnant woman [see Use in Specific Populations (8.1


                              )

                           ].
